Jo

Introduction

DXMON is a five-member boy group under H Music Entertainment (formerly NV Entertainment & SSQ Entertainment). They made their debut on January 17, 2024, with the mini album Hyperspace.

Jo has been on hiatus since June 11th, 2024 due to health concerns.

DXMON participated in ABEMA's "Re:Born" and earned 3rd place.

On September 28, 2024, it was announced that Jo would be leaving DXMON, making the team to countinue as a five-member group.
